= Mixture

The JUNO scintillator is a mixture of linear alkyl benzene (LAB), 2.5 g/L of
2,5-diphenyloxazole (PPO), 3 mg/L of 1,4-Bis(2-methylstyryl)benzene (Bis-MSB) as
wavelength shifter and 42.7 mg/L butylated hydroxytoluene (BHT) as
antioxidant@abusleme_initial_2025.

